query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(dd ss s) NoNestLoop(dd s ss i) */ select i.i_item_id,
s.s_state,
grouping(s.s_state) AS g_state,
avg(ss.ss_quantity) AS agg1,
avg(ss.ss_list_price) AS agg2,
avg(ss.ss_coupon_amt) AS agg3,
avg(ss.ss_sales_price) AS agg4
from date_dim AS dd
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_sold_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk AND dd.d_year = 1998
inner join store AS s
on ss.ss_store_sk = s.s_store_sk AND s.s_state IN ('TN',
'TN',
'TN',
'TN',
'TN',
'TN')
inner join item AS i
on ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk
inner join customer_demographics AS cd
on ss.ss_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk AND cd.cd_gender = 'F' AND cd.cd_marital_status = 'W' AND cd.cd_education_status = 'Primary' group by rollup(i.i_item_id, s.s_state) order by i.i_item_id, s.s_state LIMIT 100;
